<div id="review_2986373670" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2986373670" />
    <a title="Joy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1592683-joy"><img alt="Joy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1232335580p2/1592683.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2986373670?book_show_action=true">Sep 22, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joy" href="/user/show/1592683-joy">Joy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780743474931" href="/book/show/512984.The_Convivial_Codfish">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2986373670" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15199517357137893899">A Christmas party held by the Convivial Codfish drinking and jokester group is broken up by a train accident and a mass poisoning. Evidently clearing the decks for this, Sarah&apos;s Uncle Jem has been laid up in the hospital, and he sent his new nephew-in-law Max to the party in his place. Max&apos;s sharp eyes see things only Uncle Jem could have expected to see. Now he has to find out which of the Codfish members thinks murder is a great joke.<br/><br/>Read 2 times</span>
